<!-- OVERVIEW -->
<section>
  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <span class="tag">Business Analysis | Product Thinking | AI Systems</span>

  <p>
    MySanity is a conceptual AI-powered wellbeing and productivity platform designed to help users
    understand behavioural patterns across mood, focus, and productivity.
  </p>

  <p>
    This case study demonstrates end-to-end Business Analysis capability including requirements definition,
    user journey design, and MVP scoping.
  </p>
</section>

<!-- PROBLEM -->
<section>
  <h2>Problem Statement</h2>

  <p>
    Modern users struggle with fragmented tools for productivity and wellbeing. Task management apps focus
    only on output, while wellbeing apps focus only on mood — with no integration between the two.
  </p>

  <p>
    This leads to:
  </p>

  <ul>
    <li>Lack of insight into productivity vs mental state</li>
    <li>Disconnected tools with no unified system</li>
    <li>Limited behavioural awareness over time</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<!-- OBJECTIVES -->
<section>
  <h2>Objectives</h2>

  <ul>
    <li>Design a unified system combining productivity + wellbeing tracking</li>
    <li>Enable users to understand behavioural patterns over time</li>
    <li>Provide AI-driven insights and recommendations</li>
    <li>Define a clear MVP for initial product development</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<!-- USERS -->
<section>
  <h2>User Groups</h2>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Working Professionals:</strong> Managing workload and burnout risk</li>
    <li><strong>Students:</strong> Balancing focus, study, and mental wellbeing</li>
    <li><strong>Self-improvement users:</strong> Tracking habits and performance trends</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<!-- REQUIREMENTS -->
<section>
  <h2>Business Requirements</h2>

  <h3>Functional Requirements</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Daily mood and productivity check-in</li>
    <li>Behaviour tracking dashboard</li>
    <li>AI-generated insights and recommendations</li>
    <li>Trend analysis over time</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Non-Functional Requirements</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Data privacy and secure storage</li>
    <li>Fast response system performance</li>
    <li>Simple and intuitive user experience</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<!-- USER JOURNEY -->
<section>
  <h2>User Journey</h2>

  <ul>
    <li>User logs into system</li>
    <li>Completes daily mood + productivity check-in</li>
    <li>System captures behavioural data</li>
    <li>AI processes patterns and correlations</li>
    <li>User receives insights and recommendations</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<!-- MVP -->
<section>
  <h2>MVP Scope</h2>

  <h3>Included in MVP</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Daily check-in system</li>
    <li>Basic dashboard</li>
    <li>Simple AI insights</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Future Enhancements</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Predictive burnout detection</li>
    <li>Calendar integrations</li>
    <li>Advanced AI coaching system</li>
  </ul>
</section>

